org.apache.beam.sdk.metrics

Interface MetricCell<UserT extends Metric,DataT>

  • Type Parameters:
    UserT - The type of the user interface for reporting changes to this cell.
    DataT - The type of metric data stored (and extracted) from this cell.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CounterCell, DistributionCell

    @Experimental(value=METRICS)
public interface MetricCell<UserT extends Metric,DataT>
    A MetricCell is used for accumulating in-memory changes to a metric. It represents a specific metric name in a single context.
